tags.name: a11y-menu-button
tags.description:
`a11y-menu-button`
A toggle button for an property in the editable-table interface (editable-table.html).

Events:

  * `change` {`CustomEvent<this>`} - 

Attributes:

  * `active-item` - Whether toggle is disabled

  * `disabled` {`boolean`} - Whether toggle is disabled

  * `toggled` {`boolean`} - Whether the button is toggled

  * `focus` {`boolean`} - Whether the button is toggled

  * `hover` {`boolean`} - Whether the button is toggled

  * `disabled` {`boolean`} - Whether toggle is disabled

  * `toggled` {`boolean`} - Whether the button is toggled

  * `hover` {`boolean`} - Whether the button is toggled
